lead_paragraph: Formula One bosses would get it wrong even if they were selling ice cream and everybody wanted one flavor, Sebastian Vettel said on Thursday as the sport's qualifying format drew further criticism.

headline.print_headline: Vettel in Less Than Fine Fettle Over Qualifying
headline.main: Vettel in Less Than Fine Fettle Over Qualifying
